metadata.name: DARE TO BE
metadata.description:
Dare to be,  
To be free, to be you  
Let the world see you for the gem you are  
Let out the shine, show them who you are  
Own your past, live your moments, embrace your future  
For when the end comes calling, the memories come crashing  
Will your lips break into a smile? Or your eyes let out a tear? 
To this end, be at the helm, be the captain of your life  
Go on adventurous voyages, sail to farthest ends to find your dream  
Dearest reader, I challenge you  
Stand firm in the face of pain and fear  
Daring to be you.  
Daring to be true.
